node.title: Doing my stuff after the work

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AC on August 12, 2021. May be an anime-style image of 1 person.

node.text:
more #peterpannobouken stuff!
I wanted to make something more complex than just characters studies, before saying goodbye to these guys and moving on.
It took me some days to put all together.
Also, I tried to give some retro touch to this piece.
many characters are missing, but finding the right references was very difficult.
It's a pretty obscure anime!
.
.
.
